43
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:13,569
Taiwan has been trying for years to join the
UN,

44
00:02:13,569 --> 00:02:15,840
and China has been trying for years to block
them

45
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,200
from joining the UN.

46
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,650
In fact, this religious freedom meeting

47
00:02:19,650 --> 00:02:22,239
