that blew up one of their own satellites.

176
00:08:00,770 --> 00:08:03,070
And created a giant cloud of space debris.

177
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:05,940
That’s something NASA’s head says they’re
going to fight.

178
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:07,580
